### Get all skills
GET http://localhost:5000/api/skills
Content-Type: application/json

### Search skills by name
GET http://localhost:5000/api/skills?search=javascript&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Create (or upsert) a new skill
POST http://localhost:5000/api/skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "JavaScript"
}

### Create another skill
POST http://localhost:5000/api/skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Python"
}

### Get popular skills
GET http://localhost:5000/api/skills/popular
Content-Type: application/json
